    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-7 col-sm-12">
        <h2 class="font-weight-bold">Step. 1</h2>
        <hr />
        <p class="mt-1">For 20 minutes boil as many shredded Oyster Mushroom as possible</p>

        <h2 class="font-weight-bold">Step. 2</h2>
        <hr />
        <p class="mt-1">
          Make the Marinade Sauce of your dreams!The style + taste is up to you
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-weight-bold">Step. 3</h2>
        <hr />
        <p class="mt-1">
          Both of you should rest a littlebit
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-weight-bold">Step. 4</h2>
        <hr />
        <p class="mt-1">
          Whisk the Marinade in gently and put it in the fridge for 24 hours
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-weight-bold">Step. 5</h2>
        <hr />
        <p class="mt-1">
          Place them next to each other and put them in a fruit dryer or the owen
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-weight-bold">Step. 6</h2>
        <hr />
        <p class="mt-1">
          Dry them on around 50°C for about 7-8 hours
        </p>

        <h2>Step. 7</h2>
        <hr />
        <p class="mt-1">Yes, that's right!Around 7-8 hours!
                        If you only have oven,
                        set it on lowest and
                        leave the door open a bit
                        so the steam can leave.
                        <br>
                      At this stage
                      you can be ready!
                      or! - start melting
                      some chocolate...
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-weight-bold">Step. 8</h2>
        <hr />
        <p class="mt-1">Dip them in the nicest
                        melted chocolate you have
                        and let them cool down.
                        <br>
                        Warning:
                        by the time you finish,
                        the jerky might also be..
                        Even if you have started
                        with many kilograms
                        of mushroom, in this form
                        it will disappear
                        in no time!
        </p>
